AddressInfo.Title: 41 Rue Beauvau
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Dear openchargemap.org Executive,

Outbreak hit the economy very hard. Some companies are shut down. In this difficult situation we can help you breathe.

We provide very fast loans if you satisfy the following criteria:

* If you are US citizen or a permanent resident, and over the age of 18.
* If your income is higher than $1,000/month after tax deductions.
* If you have a checking account in your name.
* And if you have a valid  phone number/email.

If you satisfy above criteria, just fill the query form in our site. And we will get in contact with you and your loan will be approved in several hours.

Please follow the link for the form submission: https://tinyurl.com/y4zmxjpo

IMPORTANT: Please do not apply if you do not satisfy above criteria. Thank you for your understanding.


Kind Regards,
James SMITH 
JET LOANS
